Package com.shaji.HMS.model

Class Appointment

java.lang.Object
com.shaji.HMS.model.Appointment
@Entity
public class Appointment
extends java.lang.Object
The class is an entity named appointment. Appointment class stores applicationId, doctorId, applicationDate, applicationTime, patientId and applicationStatus. It helps to fetch the appointment data, whenever it is required.
